        "username": "Vinobianco",
        "uid": "93938"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t考研考公热也就这10年的事 往前推15年是中国互联网民企火红的年代 再往前推20年外企正当热 考研考公凸显社会的价值取向 也可以说是种无奈\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-18",
      "agree_count": 7,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "656310",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "对不起伤害了你",
        "uid": "104840"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudm9hY2hpbmVzZS5jb20vYS9oZS1xaW5nLWxpYW4tMjAxNDA5MTEvMjQ0NzAxNS5odG1s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/he-qing-lian-20140911/2447015.html\">何清涟：1992与2014：官员下海潮缘由比较</a><br/>\n<br/>\n让我们怀念一下曾经的“下海潮”，那个时候<mark>支人</mark>还是有勇气扔掉，而且乐于扔掉铁饭碗的。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-05-18",
